1. Hvatam *loptu* u igri fudbala. (I'm catching the ball in a game of football.)
2. On je brz u hvatanju *znanja*. (He is quick in grasping knowledge.)
3. Mama me je hvatala za ruku dok smo prelazili ulicu. (Mom was holding my hand while we were crossing the street.)
4. Moramo hvatati *trenutak* i iskoristiti ga na najbolji način. (We need to seize the moment and make the most of it.)
5. Lovac je *uhvatio* divlju svinju u šumi. (The hunter caught a wild boar in the forest.)
6. Ova knjiga me je *uhvatila* od prve stranice. (This book hooked me from the first page.)
7. Ne znam kako ću *uhvatiti* autobus ako ne krenem odmah. (I don't know how I'll catch the bus if I don't leave right away.)
8. Ulovio sam *veliku ribu* u jezeru. (I caught a big fish in the lake.)
9. Ona *hvata* tramvaj svakog jutra u 7 sati. (She catches the tram every morning at 7 o'clock.)
10. Policija je *uhvatila* pljačkaša nakon opsežne potrage. (The police caught the robber after an extensive search.)